{"title":"Amazon DynamoDB","description":"This dashboard visualizes your DynamoDB latency, error rates, and the percentage of your provisioned capacity currently in use, helping you spot changes that could affect the performance and cost of your database. For more information:\n\n- [DynamoDB integration documentation](https://docs.datadoghq.com/integrations/amazon_dynamodb/)\n\n- [DynamoDB metrics](https://www.datadoghq.com/blog/top-dynamodb-performance-metrics/)\n\n- [How to collect DynamoDB metrics](https://www.datadoghq.com/blog/how-to-collect-dynamodb-metrics/)\n\n- [How Medium monitors DynamoDB performance](https://www.datadoghq.com/blog/how-medium-monitors-dynamodb-performance/)\n\nClone this template dashboard to make changes and add your own graph widgets.","widgets":[{"id":0,"layout":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":32,"height":11},"definition":{"type":"image","url":"/static/images/logos/amazon-dynamodb_avatar.svg","sizing":"fit","margin":"large"}},{"id":1,"layout":{"x":64,"y":0,"width":28,"height":11},"definition":{"title":"Throttled requests","title_size":"16","title_align":"left","time":{"live_span":"1h"},"type":"query_value","requests":[{"conditional_formats":[{"comparator":"<=","palette":"white_on_green","value":0}],"response_format":"scalar","queries":[{"data_source":"metrics","name":"query1","query":"sum:aws.dynamodb.throttled_requests{*}.fill(zero)","aggregator":"max"}]}],"autoscale":true,"text_align":"center","custom_links":[],"precision":0}},{"id":2,"layout":{"x":34,"y":58,"width":12,"height":14},"definition":{"type":"note","content":"[Errors](https://www.datadoghq.com/blog/top-dynamodb-performance-metrics/#errors)","background_color":"gray","font_size":"18","text_align":"center","show_tick":true,"tick_pos":"50%","tick_edge":"right"}},{"id":3,"layout":{"x":48,"y":58,"width":44,"height":14},"definition":{"title":"System Errors","title_size":"16","title_align":"left","show_legend":false,"legend_size":"0","time":{"live_span":"4h"},"type":"timeseries","requests":